  <h3>ITIL SO Request Fulfulment</h3>
  <p><i><a href="/home/itilso">Back to ITIL Service Operation</a></i></p>
  <p><a href="/homeviewpdf/resources/sosummary.pdf#page=21" target="_blank">Awesome summary of this process</a></p>
