  <p><b><span id="Overview">Objective:</span></b> <span id="md-webpage-description" itemprop="description"><i>ITIL Request Fulfilment</i> aims to fulfill Service Requests, which in most cases are minor (standard) Changes - e.g. requests to change a password or requests for information.</span></p>
  <p><b>Part of</b>: Service Operation </p>
  <p><b>Process Owner</b>: Incident Manager </p>
